welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Huntington Park, the charming city known for its vibrant culture and friendly residents. Get ready to explore and immerse yourself in all that this beautiful city has to offer. Enjoy your stay!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Whiteman Airport serves as the hub for all commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Whiteman Airport caters to private and chartered flights, providing a luxurious and exclusive experience for passengers.

wifi.note: Passengers can access free WiFi throughout the airport terminal.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Torrance Airport, serving domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: A separate terminal for private and charter flights.

wifi.note: Free wifi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Long Beach Municipal Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: North Terminal
terminals.description: The North Terminal at Long Beach Municipal Airport serves primarily domestic flights.

wifi.note: Passengers can enjoy free WiFi throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Santa Ynez Airport handles all commercial flights and passenger services.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Santa Ynez Airport caters to private and charter flights.

wifi.note: Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Van Nuys Airport serves all commercial flights and provides amenities for passengers.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Van Nuys Airport caters to private and charter flights, offering a luxurious and exclusive experience for travelers.

wifi.note: Passengers can connect to the airport's free WiFi network for internet access.

terminals.name: Terminal A
terminals.description: This terminal primarily serves domestic flights for major airlines such as American Airlines and Delta.

terminals.name: Terminal B

wifi.note: Free wifi is available throughout the airport.
